text:
Guardians of the Galaxy vol. 2: The Best Lines From Trailer 3 Kofi Outlaw Start Slideshow Slide of 
One of the reasons that the Guardians of the Galaxy movie franchise has become the breakout hit that it is, is due to director James Gunn's equally dynamic skill as a script writer. Gunn's work on Guardians ' wordplay (with help from a great ensemble cast) has created all sorts of quotables and memes - and Vol. 2 looks like it will deliver even more great lines that will live on the Internet long after the film is in theaters. 
Just looking at Guardians of the Galaxy trailer #3 (which hit the web last night), there are already a bunch of great lines stuck in our head! Here are The 5 Best Lines from Guardians of the Galaxy vol. 2 Trailer #3.
